===Etymology===
From Latin '''[[inflatio]]''', ''expansion'', noun of process from perfect passive participle '''[[inflatus]]''', ''expanded'' or ''blown up'', from verb '''[[inflare]]''', ''blow into'' or ''expand'', from '''[[in-]]''', ''into'', + '''[[flare]]''', ''blow''

